      <![CDATA[<br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>To get rid of repetitive actions, I built some small Python programs with Codex to help me. Then I thought since I've built them, why not push them to GitHub?<br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>Here they are. Maybe that's why I can always find some small, strange but useful tools on GitHub that do some ununsual or even weird tasks.<br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>Of course there are apps that can do the same jobs but they are either too complicated for a small task or not free. One of them even asked me to watch ads before using shamelessly.<br><a href="/something/img/screenshots/others/github_profile.png" data-fancybox="030626" style="width:75%; display:block; margin:10px auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/something/img/screenshots/others/github_profile_thumb.webp" alt="github_profile" style="width:100%;"></a><span style="float: right;">— 3 June 2026</span><br><hr><br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>Painted some icons.<br><a href="/something/img/screenshots/others/neco_icons.png" data-fancybox="030626" style="width:75%; display:block; margin:10px auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/something/img/screenshots/others/neco_icons_thumb.webp" alt="neco_icons" style="width:100%;"></a><span style="float: right;">— 3 June 2026</span><br><hr><br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>こなかちゃん可愛いいね<br><a href="/something/img/screenshots/others/konaka_wallpaper_sunrise.png" data-fancybox="030626" style="width:75%; display:block; margin:10px auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/something/img/screenshots/others/konaka_wallpaper_sunrise_thumb.webp" alt="konaka_wallpaper_sunrise" style="width:100%;"></a><span style="float: right;">— 3 June 2026</span><br><hr><br><span style="margin-left:2em;"></span>New music collected!<a href="/something/img/screenshots/others/feishin_new_030626.png" data-fancybox="030626" style="width:75%; display:block; margin:10px auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="/something/img/screenshots/others/feishin_new_030626_thumb.webp" alt="feishin_new_030626" style="width:100%;"></a><span style="float: right;">— 3 June 2026</span><br>]]>
